messages.message: Thanks! @jack.robbins! With that said, are we good to communicate to customers that they can leverage the same APIs from the legacy platform in AI Hub, with the caveats noted? Also, are there plans to create updated APIs specifically designed for AI Hub?

Yeah, just as long as those caveats are provided. We've wanted to pull EPD-3465 in for the past few quarters but we've always needed to have our eng. resources to focus on blocker customer deliverables.
